data.description: ADORABLE home nestled in a popular and quiet area of Leeds that's gaining attention quickly. 3 Bedroom and 2 Bath home with cathedral ceiling has an expansive flow and incredible light. New floors and paint. The commute from the home is quite an experience- an incredible way to begin and conclude your day with wildlife, farms and nature abound to set the tone for a peaceful, grateful day.
